column5: Nice going!!!,.Great day for the kids for sure!!!!!!

I enjoy all of your reports as of late. I'm excitted to see the Meegs i picked up at the fishing show work  are you on a team for he tournament this year? if not you could save a team with all these white fish you are catching if you aren't on a team you are more then welcome on team 6 lol

Good job. Its been a tough year for me compared to the last 5. They dont seem to want the williams and rapalas i usually do well on. How are you working the Meegs? Tap bottom, slowly lift up and then drop back down when you mark fish?
Great day out my friend :-D We'll do it again real soon, only a few more weeks left now. Cheers until next time, Jesse
Great stuff, those are some chunky whities, the kids must have had a blast watching on screen!
Looks like you had a great day. Nice whities!

I enjoy all of your reports as of late. I'm excitted to see the Meegs i picked up at the fishing show work  are you on a team for he tournament this year? if not you could save a team with all these white fish you are catching if you aren't on a team you are more then welcome on team 6 lol  DB,  not too sure how the team structure thing works and I am definitely not on any team.  Cheers, Ice Fisherman
DB,  not too sure how the team structure thing works and I am definitely not on any team.  Cheers, Ice Fisherman  you just have to sign up on the sign up thread if you feel like  joining
That's awesome, the smiles on the kids face say it all.
